 <span data-ttu-id="7cfe3-111">Créez le package Oracle suivant sur le serveur Oracle.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7cfe3-111">Create the following Oracle package on the Oracle server.</span></span>  
  
```  
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE CURSPKG AS   
   TYPE T_CURSOR IS REF CURSOR;   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_ONE_CURSOR (N_EMPNO IN NUMBER,   
      IO_CURSOR IN OUT T_CURSOR);   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_TWO_CURSORS (EMPCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR,   
